* Commands

** Install
yay -S i3 i3status dmenu

**Enable tap to click
sudo mkdir -p /etc/X11/xorg.conf.d && sudo tee <<'EOF' /etc/X11/xorg.conf.d/90-touchpad.conf 1> /dev/null
Section "InputClass"
        Identifier "touchpad"
        MatchIsTouchpad "on"
        Driver "libinput"
        Option "Tapping" "on"
EndSection

EOF

**Natural scrolling

yay -S xorg-xinput

xinput list

showed the touchpad was id 11

xinput list-props 11

showed natural scrolling option

exec --no-startup-id xinput set-prop 11 304 1

set the option

**Caps is escape

exec --no-startup-id setxkbmap -option caps:escape

**workspace navigation
yay -S cargo
cargo install i3switcher

